title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 8 2022

description:
NFL news: Aaron Rodgers signs biggest-ever NFL contract with Packers, Russell Wilson traded to Broncos. Biden lies about his energy record. Escalation: Poland to send fighter jets to Germany. Trump predicted $7 dollar a gallon gas under Biden, blue checks mocked him. Psaki attacks Florida Surgeon General on covid shots. McDonald's closes all locations in Russia. Russophobia sweeps globe. Clay's vacation plans. Clay explains to Buck how NCAA tournament brackets work. C&B take a call to end the show.
